534
00:49:50,000 --> 00:49:53,000
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, početkom 2019.

535
00:49:53,000 --> 00:49:54,000
[SPEAKER_01] Sredinom 2019.

536
00:49:54,000 --> 00:49:55,000
[SPEAKER_01] To je bio zadnji zid.

537
00:49:55,000 --> 00:50:00,000
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, od onda, ok, bila je kriza prošle godine, ovako covid i to, to je bilo gadno.

538
00:50:00,000 --> 00:50:06,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ali nisam lupio u zid, u smisla da sam se raspao, nego jednostavno dohvatila kriza, bilo mi je teško.

539
00:50:06,000 --> 00:50:10,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ali zadnji baš ovo, da sam kresnu u zid i bilo je tamo sredinom 2019.

540
00:50:10,000 --> 00:50:14,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kad sam baš ono na aerodrobu, sam rekao bio Lego na pod i rekao, take me.

541
00:50:14,000 --> 00:50:16,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ono, gotovo sam, bože, uzmi me.

542
00:50:16,000 --> 00:50:21,000
[SPEAKER_01] Nisam imao snage, doslovno, nisam imao snage za doći do gejta.

543
00:50:21,000 --> 00:50:22,000
[SPEAKER_01] Bio sam satran.

544
00:50:22,000 --> 00:50:23,000
[SPEAKER_01] Pa to je bio...

545
00:50:23,000 --> 00:50:24,000
[SPEAKER_00] Si bio sam.

546
00:50:24,000 --> 00:50:25,000
[SPEAKER_01] Da.

547
00:50:25,000 --> 00:50:29,000
[SPEAKER_01] To je bilo, ne znam, tipa 30. putovanja u mjesec dana.

548
00:50:29,000 --> 00:50:31,000
[SPEAKER_01] Doslovno u 45 dana.

549
00:50:31,000 --> 00:50:33,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ne znam koji let.

550
00:50:33,000 --> 00:50:39,000
[SPEAKER_01] Bez dana odmora, bez spavanja, znači, baš ono, užas.

551
00:50:39,000 --> 00:50:41,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ne bi se hitio vratiti iz kraju u taj pedij.

552
00:50:41,000 --> 00:50:44,000
[SPEAKER_01] Baš sam Lego, bio sam par izu na aerodromu.

553
00:50:44,000 --> 00:50:47,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tamo sam pored nekog gejta, kak je cijeli aerodrom, tepihom.

554
00:50:47,000 --> 00:50:50,000
[SPEAKER_01] Stavio torbu sa strane Lego na pod i rekao:

555
00:50:50,000 --> 00:50:53,000
[SPEAKER_01] Sad ću silom, ja sad trebam tu leža dok ne dođem sebi.

556
00:50:53,000 --> 00:50:57,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ima sam išao tamo povest neki steak kasnije, da energiju neku vratim.

557
00:50:57,000 --> 00:51:00,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ali tu sam lupio zid, onda mi je, ne znam, puko zub.

558
00:51:00,000 --> 00:51:04,000
[SPEAKER_01] Išao sam kasnije na par operacija tog istog zuba.

559
00:51:04,000 --> 00:51:07,000
[SPEAKER_01] Vuko godinu dana, to još uvijek vučem.

560
00:51:07,000 --> 00:51:09,000
