561
00:51:09,000 --> 00:51:17,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ali zato što nisam dosao, nisam tri mjeseca, četiri, nisam stao, ali sam bio celoveno šestem brzini.

562
00:51:17,000 --> 00:51:22,000
