614
00:59:25,000 --> 00:59:28,000
[SPEAKER_01] Jel, ne možeš, ne možeš sam.

615
00:59:28,000 --> 00:59:32,000
[SPEAKER_00] Nutricionist, kuhar, mentalni trener.

616
00:59:32,000 --> 00:59:37,000
